title: A Level Sociology - Types of Questionnaires
description: Liz looks at questionnaire types for your A Level Sociology exam. In this episode, she will look at structured, open-ended and self-completion questionnaires. Ideal for preparing for your A Level Sociology exam. For more info visit www.senecalearning.com
